nt": " We haven't ever seen real battle on this continent since the Civil war. None of us (except those in military service) have a clue on how to fight this threat! We need to stop and drop the delusion that If We just continue living our lives, work hard, provide for our families, then everything will be OK and somehow blow over. (The ostrich analogy comes to mind.)\n\nWe need a \"Domestic Patton\", to wake us from our malaise, and provide an achievable plan to defeat the destructive element that has invaded our shores.\n\nThere, that's off my chest. Who wants to play Canasta!", "author": "Spunas1", "created": 1782306043509, "profile_picture": "5EfFgwxaSlrQ", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Spunas1", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "These people (Islam - the real threat) smell the blood in the water. (due to our inaction towards the threat) ", "last_comment_created": 1782311065120, "content": "<p>We haven't ever seen real battle on this continent since the Civil war. None of us (except those in military service) have a clue on how to fight this threat! We need to stop and drop the delusion that If We just continue living our lives, work hard, provide for our families, then everything will be OK and somehow blow over. (The ostrich analogy comes to mind.)</p>\n<p>We need a &quot;Domestic Patton&quot;, to wake us from our malaise, and provide an achievable plan to defeat the destructive element that has invaded our shores.</p>\n<p>There, that's off my chest. Who wants to play Canasta!</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 12, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": f